{"tid":1876730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印尼2.6億人口卻零肺炎之迷","createTime":"2020-02-12T14:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T16:31:38.000Z","uid":25468,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bdbfb811ed9cfa5db5469b97ed631f1f942fc5c4","tid":1876730,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vd1LT0zgwygClA4vO71p9A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyODA7aD03MjA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/QgePCu1Y7Gun.Z2nRpEpYQ--~B/aD01NzY7dz0xMDI0O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ftvn.com.tw/715c3d94c55c6669ee7b25a78cb30ced\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVd1LT0zgwygClA4vO71p9A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyODA7aD03MjA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQgePCu1Y7Gun.Z2nRpEpYQ--~B%2FaD01NzY7dz0xMDI0O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fftvn.com.tw%2F715c3d94c55c6669ee7b25a78cb30ced&h=a91ed899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎爆發至今，東南亞至少已有五國確診，其中新加坡的46例，還是境外、除日本第二高的國家。但新加坡的隔海鄰居，並擁有2.6億人口的印尼卻至今是零病例。不少人就懷疑，印尼是不是根本沒檢驗，而印尼衛生部門則說，從武漢撤回的兩百多名印尼僑胞都很健康，而且<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">檢驗費用太昂貴，所以真的沒檢驗</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n車站外頭，部分民眾還是戴著口罩，武漢肺炎爆發超過一個月，疫情蔓延全球，就是東南亞國家都至少有5國確診，但擁有2.6億人口，又是東南亞運輸中心的印尼，竟然至今維持零確診。<br />\n<br />\n有雅加達居民說：「身為印尼人我相信政府，目前這裡就是沒有新冠病毒的確診案例。」<br />\n<br />\n有人相信政府好厲害，不過，也有人質疑到底是如何辦到。有印尼民眾說：「有可能也許我們的政府，沒有辦法檢測出病毒的症狀，也許他們可以，但他們沒有適合的設備檢驗.....。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/9e34d1b3-eda6-4ca4-8874-7011b7cc7d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2F9e34d1b3-eda6-4ca4-8874-7011b7cc7d89.jpg&h=3bfce114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懷疑政府根本沒檢驗，實際上也確實如此。因為印尼衛生部官員已證實，2日從中國武漢撤回的243名僑民通通都很健康，沒人發燒、咳嗽、流鼻水，所以不需要檢測；同時也說，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">檢測大批隔離者，需要至少10億印尼盾，相當於台幣約250萬元，但檢驗至少要兩次才準確，費用太昂貴，所以經考慮，決定還是免檢測。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/d84e79e0-a4aa-41f9-8fce-f18e6180d5a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2Fd84e79e0-a4aa-41f9-8fce-f18e6180d5a1.jpg&h=ffb2427b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11日衛生部官員召開記者會，雲淡風輕表示已經準備好100家醫院待命，而且全國34省，每一省都至少有一家醫院，可收納治療新冠狀病毒的病患。不過，都跳過了檢驗程序，哪裡會有確診案例呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020212I06M1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2020212I06M1&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=bf83ada8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020212I06M1</a>"},{"pid":"5cc87c3072b2b5de3ded1f7f2504e45712896695","tid":1876730,"uid":104138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:52:19.000Z","msg":"10億印尼盾好少咋wo..."},{"pid":"fb0e283e7f6461af6468a28c6d3def9234e17c0e","tid":1876730,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76586e417fcc8bdb7fcc763f1c81d72b6b6272e","tid":1876730,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:52:53.000Z","msg":"又燈"},{"pid":"0fad477eee29c05b86a1508313f6774f7948d311","tid":1876730,"uid":67425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a76586e417fcc8bdb7fcc763f1c81d72b6b6272e","tid":1876730,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:52:53.000Z","msg":"又燈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"上次先燈完西藏"},{"pid":"b65d5c8016aa31654faa173b22fe7fe3fb106bb4","tid":1876730,"uid":177089,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-